{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774300/extras/topheader.gif?t=1732809394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this fast-paced action game you dodge and parry enemy attacks with your cursor. You can generate resources on the board by parrying their attacks. The resources all have different abilities to help you defeat the enemies.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is <strong>hard</strong> and to succeed you will need good reflex and familiarity with the enemies' skills and attack patterns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>You've been warned, good luck!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774300/extras/weaponsheader.gif?t=1732809394\" />Unlock different characters and their unique weapons. Every weapon has their distinct play style and skill tree.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774300/extras/skillsheader.gif?t=1732809394\" />Over 100 unlockable skills for you to discover and combine. Adapt to your situation and create your own unique build every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774300/extras/blocksheader.gif?t=1732809394\" />Weapons will have different resources (block types) that can help you defeat the enemies. You will also come across special blocks throughout each run, these could be chests, companions, environmental, buff and de-buffs. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All enemies have their own set of skills and attack patterns that appear on the board as <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774300/extras/blockcountdown.png?t=1732809394\" />. You need to parry their attacks to generate resources that will help you defeat the enemy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Perfect Parries</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A regular parry will trigger the cooldown, but when you perform the parry near the very end of an attack it is a <strong>perfect parry.</strong>\u00a0these will not consume a charge. Timing enemy attack patterns to chain perfect parries will be the key to success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2774300/extras/perfectparry.gif?t=1732809394\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Stage One Cleared?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2774300/d681c22e5fa898f7e4b3ce6702cea8986d72a16e.jpg"},{"name":"Stage One Cleared!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2774300/bc68a34a31a34236054985755d84b258eedaa240.jpg"},{"name":"Stage Two Cleared?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2774300/87d0f840f86d989e85f3abbd453240f0f59cfccf.jpg"},{"name":"Stage Two Cleared!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2774300/b1e44af3003ea9613177f7c4330b4608741e63c8.jpg"},{"name":"Stage Three Cleared?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2774300/94eaa1ec8bda3b0b151e596f8b89990babb38346.jpg"},{"name":"Stage Three Cleared!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2774300/524b788dbe3a4a428cecb768a28ceded167e4b23.jpg"},{"name":"Stage Four Cleared?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2774300/ded203535ab1ff64bbd3917b50a8b28059afe0c6.jpg"},{"name":"Stage Four Cleared!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2774300/ba38301014b